# Advanced Python Logging & Monitoring

This project demonstrates advanced logging, decorators, time measurement, and file-based history tracking in Python.

âœ… Features:
- Logs every run into `app.log`
- Measures function execution time using a custom decorator
- Stores execution history in `history.json`
- Handles invalid user input (no crash)
- Fully expandable for real-world apps

## How to run

python main.py

## Example Output
- User enters a number
- Program creates a list from 1..n
- Execution time is logged
- History is saved to JSON

## Technologies Used
- logging
- json
- functools (decorators)
- time
